data.description: Discover serenity and space in this charming 4 bedroom, 2 bath home nestled on over 3 acres, that is just a stone's throw away from the picturesque Pike Lake.  Step into the heart of modern comfort and style with the open concept main level of this home.  Sunlight streams through large windows, illuminating the spacious living area, seamlessly flowing into the dining space and inviting kitchen.  The sleek design and thoughtful layout make entertaining a delight, with guests easily mingling between rooms.  Descending to the walk out lower level, you're greeted by a sprawling family room with gas fireplace, that will be perfect for movie nights, game days, or simply unwinding with loved ones.   Step outside onto the screened in porch, where tranquility meets convenience.   Enjoy the fresh air as you host summer BBQ's or maybe just enjoy your cup of coffee in the morning.  This versatile space invites you to embrace the beauty of outdoor, rain or shine.  In addition to your porch you have the expansive deck to enjoy our springtime weather coming soon.  Boasting two garages, this property offers ample storage for vehicles, equipment, and recreational gear.  Enjoy the beauty of nature and the convenience of modern living in this idylic retreat where peaceful surroundings and outdoor adventures await at your doorstep.  Schedule up your showing today before your next home is gone.
